{"title":"取消Chrome和Firefox的更新提示","slug":"取消Chrome和Firefox的更新提示","date":"2022-11-27T11:56:56.000Z","updated":"2022-11-27T12:03:55.394Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/取消Chrome和Firefox的更新提示.json","excerpt":"最新的浏览器都在设置里面取消了自动更新的设置，本文介绍如何取消Chrome和Firefox这两款浏览器的更新提示。","covers":null,"content":"<p>最新的浏览器都在设置里面取消了自动更新的设置，本文介绍如何取消Chrome和Firefox这两款浏览器的更新提示。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"应用环境\"><a href=\"#应用环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"应用环境\"></a>应用环境</h2><p>OS: Windows</p>\n<p>Firefox: 102</p>\n<p>Chrome: 96</p>\n<h2 id=\"Firefox\"><a href=\"#Firefox\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Firefox\"></a>Firefox</h2><p>修改注册表，在CMD中执行以下命令即可：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">reg <span class=\"token function\">add</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Mozilla\\Firefox\"</span> /v DisableAppUpdate /t REG_DWORD /d <span class=\"token number\">1</span> /f<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>更多方法可参考<a href=\"https://sysin.org/blog/disable-firefox-auto-update/#Firefox-for-Windows\">如何禁用 Firefox 自动更新 (macOS, Linux, Windows)</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Chrome\"><a href=\"#Chrome\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Chrome\"></a>Chrome</h2><p>直接修改Chrome浏览器的快捷方式，修改target参数：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token string\">\"C:\\Program Files\\Chrome\\Chrome.exe\"</span> --disable-background-networking<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n","more":"<h2 id=\"应用环境\"><a href=\"#应用环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"应用环境\"></a>应用环境</h2><p>OS: Windows</p>\n<p>Firefox: 102</p>\n<p>Chrome: 96</p>\n<h2 id=\"Firefox\"><a href=\"#Firefox\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Firefox\"></a>Firefox</h2><p>修改注册表，在CMD中执行以下命令即可：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">reg <span class=\"token function\">add</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Policies\\Mozilla\\Firefox\"</span> /v DisableAppUpdate /t REG_DWORD /d <span class=\"token number\">1</span> /f<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>更多方法可参考<a href=\"https://sysin.org/blog/disable-firefox-auto-update/#Firefox-for-Windows\">如何禁用 Firefox 自动更新 (macOS, Linux, Windows)</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Chrome\"><a href=\"#Chrome\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Chrome\"></a>Chrome</h2><p>直接修改Chrome浏览器的快捷方式，修改target参数：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token string\">\"C:\\Program Files\\Chrome\\Chrome.exe\"</span> --disable-background-networking<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>","categories":[{"name":"系统安装配置","path":"api/categories/系统安装配置.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"系统安装配置","path":"api/tags/系统安装配置.json"}]}